# Files used for differential expression Analysis

Genetic data needed to run the code is available in NCBI under accession PRJNA818778. 

Description: 

predicted_genes - Predict gene names for transcriptomes generated using EggNOG Mapper in OmicsBox.
  June_EggNOG.tsv - June sucker
  Straw_EggNOG.tsv - Strawberry Reservoir Utah sucker
  Utah_EggNOG.tsv - Utah Lake Utah sucker
